dfischer.utils

Class NtlmConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.NtlmConfig

  • public class NtlmConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains the NTLM authentication data of a Microsoft Windows account - used by the Proxy Sniffer GUI.
